Honestly really wonderful service and food. We were walking down the boardwalk for a mile looking for just the right restaurant and this ended up being the perfect spot with something for everyone and all the food was fresh and great tasting, and the service doubled with blessing us with extra food and big portions for our party. Very kind host/hostesses and servers and went above and beyond (and were not on the street trying to coax people into their restaurant, because they knew the food and service sells as it is) The pasta dishes and sea food dishes are very tasty and all the sides and salads were a great compliment. Plan to return in the future, wonderful experience.
